headline: Square Expands Banking Services to Give Sellers Better Control of Their Cash Flow
summary: OAKLAND, Calif., April 29, 2025--Square announced new Square Banking tools that give sellers instant access to their cash flow and free, easier ways to manage their earnings. headline: Shift4 Revenue, Payment Volume Top Wall Street Targets
summary: Shift4 rose despite a Q1 earnings miss as revenue, payment volume and other key financial metrics beat Wall Street's targets.
